{
  "text": "MATERIALS AND METHODS Analytical equipment. The analytical equipment used in the luciferase assay of ATP was a modification of a device originally described by Chappelle et al. [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "85252975"
